<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.8">
<l>kuṟukā tamaṉṉaraik kūṭu kalakkiveṅ kāṉiṭaic</l>
<l>ciṟukāl neṟiyē pōkkuvik kuñcelvaṉ poṉmalai</l>
<l>yaṟukāl varivaṇṭu kaḷā yiranā mañcolli</l>
<l>ciṟukā laippāṭun teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The golden mountain of the wealthy Lord who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having destroyed the lairs of the lesser kings,</l>
<l rend="indent">drove [them] onto the narrow footpaths</l>
<l rend="indent">in the middle of the hot jungle,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South where six-legged striped bees</l>
<l rend="indent">sing [his] thousand names in the early dawn.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
